The Swap.gg Chrome Extension is the perfect companion for CS2 & Rust skin traders. With millions of active users and over 10,000 trades processed daily, Swap.gg is one of the most trusted trading platforms for Counter-Strike & Rust skins. This extension allows you to:

- Quickly navigate to important pages like your trade page, instant sell page, and trade history with one click.
- Stay connected to the platform for real-time updates on trades and market trends with our blog.
- Enjoy a faster trading experience by having all your essential links just a click away.

Whether you're a casual trader or a high-volume user, the Swap.gg Chrome extension simplifies your trading journey by giving you quick and direct access to the tools and resources you need.
